  \  AgarPaint | |------
   \___________|_|

What is it?
-----------
AgarPaint is an editor for bitmap graphics and animations. It is meant as
a convenient tool for editing pixmaps built into applications. The icons
built into Agar were generated by AgarPaint. AgarPaint is implemented as
a front-end to the Agar-RG library (http://libagar.org/rg). 

License
-------
AgarPaint is freely distributable under the same license as Agar itself,
a revised two-clause BSD license (http://libagar.org/license.html).

